OL,3,CBenjamin Mendy pays off six-figure tax
OL,4,Cdebt
OL,6,FFormer Manchester City footballer
OL,7,FBenjamin Mendy's High Court tax debt
OL,8,Fcase has come to an end after he paid
OL,9,Fa six-figure sum.
OL,11,FHM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) had
OL,12,Fsought a bankruptcy order against the
OL,13,FFrench football player over a bill
OL,14,Fpreviously said to be around #800,000.
OL,16,FAt a hearing on Monday 29 April,
OL,17,Fbefore a specialist insolvency judge,
OL,18,FMr Mendy's lawyers said the
OL,19,Foutstanding sum of just under #710,000
OL,20,Fhad been paid.
