OL,6,FHowever, Mr Doyle said he was
OL,7,Fconfident the debt would be paid
OL,8,Fpromptly.
OL,10,FHe added that Mr Mendy "won't have
OL,11,Fpicked up post and won't have realised
OL,12,Fhe's in debt to the borough council"
OL,13,Fas he has been away from the property.
OL,15,FAt a hearing in February, the court
OL,16,Fheard that Mr Mendy was bringing legal
OL,17,Faction against his former club after
OL,18,FManchester City stopped paying him
OL,19,Fwhen he was charged with rape in 2021.
