OL,6,FThe footballer was subsequently
OL,7,Fcleared of rape and attempted rape at
OL,8,FChester Crown Court.
OL,10,FMr Doyle told the hearing that Mr
OL,11,FMendy previously did not have the
OL,12,Fmoney immediately available to pay the
OL,13,Ftax debt, adding that his salary for
OL,14,FFrench club Lorient is "about one
OL,15,Ftenth" of his previous wage.
